Package ca.retrylife.inputlib.types

Class Token

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.retrylife.inputlib.types.Token
  • public class Token
extends java.lang.Object
    A Token is a representation of an input token. This class automatically handles type-conversion, so the user can just call the getters. Keep in mind that all getters are marked @Nullable
